[INTERPRETER]
{"action": "explain", "question": "Is feeling destroyed after Z5 normal?", "free_text": "I went all-out on my Z5 intervals and now I feel destroyed. Normal?"}

JOSI:
That's expected after quality Z5 work — those intervals push your oxygen delivery to the limit. The next 24-48 hours are recovery time. Your body is processing that stimulus right now. Eat well, sleep well, and tomorrow should be an easier day. If you still feel wrecked in two days, we'll know you pushed a bit beyond what your body was ready for.

